	<tr>
		<td class="bodyText">
Note that the application can be used in two modes: In <b>individual mode</b>, a user can register with their email address and then use the app. The <b>group mode</b> is expected to be used by council workers when they are doing a walk-n-talk session with a group of people in their local area. Note that the latter mode requires the council to have contacted us prior to set up the session details in our database.
